            </title>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<div class="tougao-user">感謝 IT 之家網友 <a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1677538" rel="nofollow">小伯爵</a>、<a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1822428" rel="nofollow">Mo_Onster</a> 的線索投遞！</div><p data-vmark="8814"><a class="s_tag" href="https://www.ithome.com/" target="_blank">IT 之家</a> 1 月 7 日消息，網絡上有人吐槽微信私密朋友圈有 bug，騰訊微信團隊發文致歉，並表示此 bug 已徹底修復。</p><blockquote><p data-vmark="f62d">抱歉給大家帶來困擾。1 月 1 日當天極小部分用戶發表私密朋友圈，好友可以在朋友圈看到這個用戶的頭像紅點，但無法看到具體內容。此 bug 已徹底修復。</p></blockquote><p style="text-align: center;" data-vmark="171a"><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/1/605df14b-64de-456b-b0ca-5fabad688010.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" w="802" h="180" title="微信私密朋友圈被吐槽有 bug，官方發文致歉並修復" width="802" height="180" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p data-vmark="446d">IT 之家附私密朋友圈設置流程：</p><p data-vmark="2b4e">1、進入「我的」界面，點擊朋友圈</p><p style="text-align: center;" data-vmark="60b9"><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/1/837c6c20-0568-4662-8aeb-182fd71d3c04.png?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xYy9xYzExNy5wbmc=,t_100,g_9,y_19,x_19,a_0/format,f_auto" w="1260" h="1146" data-marks="1931fd9d012eb6d1654c4481a49053b448746e2078af6e2edaa27024eb2116c52e526772c469fef9e23483843258e624" title="微信私密朋友圈被吐槽有 bug，官方發文致歉並修復" width="1260" height="746" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p data-vmark="2ed6">2、選擇「前往朋友圈」</p><p style="text-align: center;" data-vmark="3b31"><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/1/13687b2a-88c3-4464-971b-3c8b6793f2c1.png?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xYy9xYzEzOS5wbmc=,t_100,g_9,y_19,x_19,a_0/format,f_auto" w="1260" h="1703" data-marks="1931fd9d012eb6d16a52deee73444462c32d924568c8a51c6e989462353200dcdb83404b77264c2f3df21a7cfa35a3bd" title="微信私密朋友圈被吐槽有 bug，官方發文致歉並修復" width="1260" height="1108" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p data-vmark="e28c">3、點擊想要設置私密的內容</p><p st